## Phase overview

| Phase | Theme | Target window | Goal in one line |
|---|---|---|---|
| **0** | Foundation | Wk 1–2 (Jun 7–20) | Brand, design system, architecture, analytics, SEO infra — all rails laid. |
| **1** | Hero tools MVP | Wk 3–5 (Jun 21–Jul 11) | A launchable, beautiful, fast core: calculator + image analyzer + crop visualizer. |
| **2** | Dev cluster + Tier 1 | Wk 6–7 (Jul 12–25) | Win the developer/designer search cluster; ship the embeddable widget + npm package. |
| **3** | Reference + print + Tier 2 | Wk 8–9 (Jul 26–Aug 8) | Device/resolution data, PPI/print cluster, platform-size pages. |
| **4** | Monetization | Wk 10–11 (Aug 9–22) | AdSense (clean), affiliate, Pro tier — without hurting UX or CWV. |
| **5** | Scale + API + locales | Wk 12+ | Controlled Tier-3 release, paid API, localization. |
